mc_eid=3D[UNIQID]) . How to inhabit that pleasurable=2C perilous place of=
 uncertainty is what George Saunders explores throughout his conversation=
 with Deborah Eisenberg=2C found in Upstairs at the Strand: Writers in Con=
versation at the Legendary Bookstore (http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/AS=
IN/0393352080/braipick-20?mc_cid=3D1ed92b7ada&mc_eid=3D[UNIQID]) (public=
