conversation-at-the-legendary-bookstore/oclc/909974445&referer=3Dbrief_res=
ults?mc_cid=3D1ed92b7ada&mc_eid=3D[UNIQID]) ) =E2=80=94 that marvelous re=
cord of public encounters between literary titans at the Rare Book Room of=
