da&mc_eid=3D[UNIQID]) =2C A.M. Homes (https://www.brainpickings.org/2016/=
01/27/why-we-write-about-ourselves/?mc_cid=3D1ed92b7ada&mc_eid=3D[UNIQID]=
) =2C Renata Adler (https://www.brainpickings.org/2015/03/16/boredom/?mc_c=
