/04/27/ann-patchett-on-writing/?mc_cid=3D1ed92b7ada&mc_eid=3D[UNIQID])=
 =2C Neil Gaiman=E2=80=99s eight rules of writing
(https://www.brainpickings.org/2012/09/28/neil-gaiman-8-rules-of-writing/?=
